        "fPort": 85,
        "bytes": [255, 255, 0]
      },
      "expected": {
        "errors": ["no recognized Milesight channels"]
      },
      "source": "synthetic"
    }
  ],
  "downlink": [],
  "_note": "expected.data authored via the ORACLE method: synthetic inputs decoded by the normalized codec.js (expected derived from reference/upstream-codec.js semantics, not its output shape). Covers action.motion.detected true (tilt) and false (normal), the abnormal/alarming TLV variants, plus >=1 error vector. position (accelerometer tilt status) is the motion-defining event; distance is in mm (no vocab key) -> distanceMm extra; temperature -> air.temperature; battery % -> batteryPercent extra."
